OL,3,C'Hartlepool residents pay more council
OL,4,Ctax than in Westminster', says think
OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FThe partnership is calling for council
OL,8,Ftax bands to be re-evaluated, and
OL,9,Fdescribed the current situation as
OL,10,F"unfair and outdated".
OL,12,FHenri Murison, of the Northern
OL,13,FPowerhouse Partnership, said: ""The
OL,14,Fdouble challenge here is some councils
OL,15,Flike Westminster famously have some of
OL,16,Fthe lowest council tax in the country
OL,17,Fand the people who live in those areas
OL,18,Fhave also benefitted from their houses
OL,19,Fgoing up in value but them not being
OL,20,Fre-banded to catch up with the fact
OL,21,Fthey are worth a lot more.
