OL,4,Ctax than in Westminster', says think
OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,F"So there's a northern tax bombshell,
OL,8,Fbecause we haven't revalued council
OL,9,Ftax for thirty years."
OL,11,FThe partnership said a householder in
OL,12,FGateshead will see their council tax
OL,13,Fgo up by more than #116 this year,
OL,14,Fcompared to just over #45 in
OL,15,FWestminster.
OL,17,FHow does council tax banding work?
OL,19,FThere are eight council tax bands from
OL,20,FBand A - the cheapest - to Band H -
OL,21,Fthe most expensive.
