OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FCurrent bands are based on a
OL,8,Fproperty's value in 1991. A report by
OL,9,Fthe Institute of Fiscal Studies in
OL,10,F2020 said official estimates suggest
OL,11,Fthe average price in London is now
OL,12,Fmore than six times what it was in
OL,13,F1995, compared with barely three times
OL,14,Fin the North East.
OL,16,FThe same report found the most
OL,17,Fvaluable properties in 1991 attract
OL,18,Fjust three times as much tax as the
OL,19,Fleast valuable properties, despite
OL,20,Fbeing worth at least eight times as
OL,21,Fmuch in 1991.
