OL,7,FCouncils with lower quality housing
OL,8,Fstock cannot raise as much through
OL,9,Fraising taxes as councils with larger
OL,10,Fand more expensive homes.
OL,12,FMartin Gannon, leader of Gateshead
OL,13,FCouncil, said re-evaluation banding
OL,14,Fwould result in some net winners and
OL,15,Fsome net losers - but the net impact
OL,16,Fwould be a similar amount of funding
OL,17,Ffor local Government.
